channel.title: FileRSM delphi unit with v2 file support
channel.description:
Direct replacement for FileRSM unit in RSMV,RSMI,DatMaker, etc. Supports both file formats.
I know it's fugly, all the extra crap is for v2 to v1 conversion, file merging, and as usual i left in the debug tests, remove what you don't need.
Normal scan rules apply :- http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GNMODJ0W
Thought i'd post it before i completely screw it up....
